snippet.title: Catty Shack - Indie Game Trailer #2
snippet.description: This trailer has narration! "Catty Shack" is a free indie game made by Ian Burnette. It's a hand-drawn kitty collect-a-thon. Available now at: https://gamejolt.com/games/catty-shack/249613
